title: DRAMAtical Murder: Data_xx_Transitory
synopsis: Data xx Transitory is the thirteenth and bonus episode of the DRAMAtical Murder animation. It features all of the bad endings from the original game.
voices: ['Kisaichi, Atsushi', 'Hino, Satoshi', 'Nakazawa, Masatomo', 'Takahashi, Hiroki', 'Takeuchi, Ryouta', 'Matsuda, Kenichirou', 'Majima, Junji', 'Higuchi, Tomoyuki']
